  // INDOOR FLOORS — walkable tiles that quicken movement (`floorSpeed` multiplies the tile's move-cost,
  // <1 = faster) and keep an entity off the wet ground (`floorDryness` 0–1 cuts how wet the tile reads).
  // Baked onto the tile by BuildingService.applyBuildingFootprint; read by MovementSystem + the wetness
  // ticks. NOT streets — they don't bias pathing; pair with a roof to also stay dry in the rain.
